				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1\times {10}^{19}{\mathrm{cm}}^{-3}$$\end{document} doping concentration are taken into account. In between, IB is formed in the bandgap of silicon due to the embedded graphene/Si QDs SL. The solar generation rate analyzer, a functional module provided by Lumerical, is exploited to compute the electron–hole generation rate.Fig. 3
Base structure of graphene/Si QDIBSC

